1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 21

2
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:44,920
What's this?

3
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:47,840
Medical fee.

4
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:50,430
You really think

5
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,000
I brought you here to pay the bills?

6
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,510
I know.

7
00:01:59,230 --> 00:02:00,400
You're afraid I'll lose control.

8
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,400
Are you calm now?

9
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,000
I shouldn't have

10
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,030
listened to my dad.

11
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,430
We even skipped the license.

12
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,030
It goes deeper

13
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,120
than that.

14
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:16,590
I just hope

15
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,680
you learn from this.

16
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,590
And also,

17
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:23,470
take care of Dahu.

18
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,030
Don't let him blame Qian.

19
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,190
That was close!

20
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:42,120
Good thing Mr. Li was so quick.

21
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:43,190
Fang Wanzhi,

22
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,000
how could you put yourself in danger?

23
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:46,190
If something bad

24
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,030
is about to happen,

25
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,590
you should keep yourself safe

26
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,590
and call the police.

27
00:02:50,430 --> 00:02:51,310
I'm treating Xingke

28
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,470
and his girlfriend to dinner.

29
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,520
If you promise not to run your mouth,

30
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,520
I might let you tag along.

31
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:57,910
If not...

32
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,630
Get... get back to work.

33
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,590
Oh my goodness!

34
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,870
Xingke, what happens to your hand?

35
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:10,870
Don't worry.

36
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,120
It's just a small cut.

37
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,000
Wanzhi,

38
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:14,750
let me

39
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,710
introduce you.

40
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,190
This is my girlfriend,

41
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:17,800
Emily.

42
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,590
Hello.

43
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,400
I've heard a lot about you.

44
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:23,190
Nice to meet you.

45
00:03:23,910 --> 00:03:25,000
You're beautiful.

46
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:27,030
You're even more beautiful.

47
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,080
This way.

48
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:28,630
- Go.
- Okay.

49
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,590
Go.

50
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,000
Where's Qian?

51
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:38,960
She's gone.

52
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:52,080
You're something else.

53
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,520
Think you could block a knife?

54
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:56,080
If you'd been in front,

55
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:57,910
you'd have done the same.

56
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,310
How's your brother?

57
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,000
He's seriously injured.

58
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,360
But he says it's no big deal.

59
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:07,680
Is that damn Zhu gone?

60
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:08,630
Yeah.

61
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,310
He says

62
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,280
he won't bother Qian again.

63
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,560
They were never a good match.

64
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,680
A marriage built on that

65
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,270
won't survive.

66
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,310
Legally,

67
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:20,870
they were

68
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,480
never married.

69
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,270
What was Zhu thinking?

70
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:26,040
Why didn't he get the license?

71
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,040
And Qian.

72
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,950
If Liu didn't agree,

73
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,560
why did she marry Zhu

74
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,560
and have his kid?

75
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,070
It's obvious.

76
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,190
Just for the money.

77
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:41,630
She said it at Seaside Eateries.

78
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:43,600
She used the bride price to pay off debts.

79
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,480
She just looked down on herself.

80
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:47,630
And me and you.

81
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,190
You, me, and her.

82
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,390
We three lived together

83
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:51,870
in that container.

84
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:52,950
If Hao Qianqian had said

85
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,310
she was in debt

86
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,390
and being chased,

87
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,920
I would've given her

88
00:04:56,950 --> 00:04:57,800
all my money.

89
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,270
I believe you would have too.

90
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,430
But her?

91
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,680
She traded herself for that money.

92
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,360
So pathetic.

93
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:13,720
Alright,

94
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,240
this thing is over.

95
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:16,920
Don't be mad anymore.

96
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:18,160
At least,

97
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:21,070
your niece

98
00:05:21,510 --> 00:05:22,680
has got backbone.

99
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,720
She'd rather use the bride price

100
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,480
to buy her freedom

101
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,600
than give in.

102
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:28,240
Right.

103
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:32,800
Zhao Jun knows her own mind.

104
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,560
Why isn't she back yet?

105
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,720
She should be off work.

106
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,480
Is she

107
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,600
dating someone?

108
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,240
Some guys are pursuing her.

109
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,720
Don't go home tonight.

110
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,680
First the knife,

111
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,750
then the blood.

112
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,310
I'm a little scared.

113
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,070
Keep me company.

114
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,270
Hello?

115
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,480
(Is that Ms. Fang?)

116
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,950
Yes, who am I speaking with?

117
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:12,720
(Relative of Zhao Jun?)

118
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,830
(This is her manager.)

119
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,240
(Please come to Aimin Hospital.)

120
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:16,360
(Surgery emergency.)

121
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:17,480
What happened?

122
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,120
Are you Ms. Fang?

123
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,870
I'm the one who called you.

124
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,800
I'm the factory rep.

125
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,070
Call me Mr. Luo.

126
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,430
Where's Zhao Jun?

127
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,510
Zhao Jun is...

128
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,070
Hurry back! We need to talk!

129
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,070
I'm busy.

130
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,190
I don't have much time.

131
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,120
Zhao Jun.

132
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:51,480
The doctor checked her hand.

133
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:54,000
Auntie, don't look.

134
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,630
Don't move.

135
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:09,390
Don't... don't tell my mom.

136
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,190
When did this happen?

137
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,680
Two hours ago.

138
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,750
When did you arrive?

139
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,750
Only 30 minutes from the factory.

140
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,040
Where are the severed fingers?

141
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,160
We gave it to the doctor.

142
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,480
Then why isn't she in surgery yet?

143
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:23,480
The manager said

144
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,430
Zhao Jun has to sign before surgery.

145
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,630
So she told them

146
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,720
your number.

147
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,630
Auntie,

148
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,560
it hurts.

149
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,070
I'm so weak.

150
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,360
Can't think now.

151
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:38,270
Please handle this for me.

152
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:45,830
Hello.

153
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,390
I'm Zhao Jun's family.

154
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,870
Please schedule her surgery.

155
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,070
Sure, one moment.

156
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:51,120
Ms. Fang.

157
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,480
We brought the cash.

158
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:54,720
According to the rules,

159
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,750
you need to sign

160
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:57,120
this termination agreement.

161
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,040
Labor contract termination.

162
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:02,800
Waiver and indemnity form.

163
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,040
If you sign them,

164
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,070
you'll get the money.

165
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,390
Then my job here is done.

166
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,310
And you can get the surgery.

167
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,270
Even if you don't,

168
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,560
her future is secure.

169
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,680
The kid is injured.

170
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,750
Shouldn't we

171
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:13,870
save her first?

172
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,560
Ms. Fang,

173
00:08:14,830 --> 00:08:15,750
she's not a kid.

174
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:16,600
Our factory

175
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:18,390
never hires minors.

176
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,800
Unless Zhao Jun's ID was fake.

177
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:21,750
Then it's not on us.

178
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,360
Sorry.

179
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,600
That was the wrong word.

180
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,600
A worker is injured.

181
00:08:24,630 --> 00:08:26,000
Four of her fingers are severed!

182
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,680
We should

183
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,000
save her first, shouldn't we?

184
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,600
Clam down.

185
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,630
Clam down.

186
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,480
We don't have a choice.

187
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:32,480
That's how

188
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,960
we did it before.

189
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,870
But it caused trouble.

190
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,960
Dozens of relatives

191
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,960
came to make scenes.

192
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,550
Banners and sit-ins.

193
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,670
We couldn't handle it.

194
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,870
So the factory

195
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:42,910
has a new rule.

196
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,240
The first step

197
00:08:44,270 --> 00:08:45,600
is to settle compensation

198
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:47,390
and terminate the labor contract.

199
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:48,150
After that,

200
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:49,550
it's all up to

201
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,670
the injured worker

202
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:51,630
and their family.

203
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,960
Screw that rule!

204
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:00,440
I get that you're upset.

205
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,600
But anyway,

206
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:02,240
staying calm...

207
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,120
From now on,

208
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,150
all of Zhao Jun's bills

209
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:04,910
are on me.

210
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:05,840
Get her into surgery.

211
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:06,720
Okay.

212
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,870
I'll go find the doctor.

213
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:08,750
Ms. Fang.

214
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,000
Juan, once you get the order,

215
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,870
use my card to pay.

216
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,910
Ms. Fang, we...

217
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:13,390
You're being irresponsible.

218
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:15,150
I'll take legal action.

219
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,030
Wait, Ms. Fang.

220
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:17,120
At least you should know

221
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,150
how much we're offering.

222
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,200
Even if you sue us,

223
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,270
you won't get this much.

224
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,000
Get lost.

225
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:21,870
Ms. Fang,

226
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:22,670
listen to me.

227
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,080
Let's talk this through.

228
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:25,320
Get lost!

229
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,030
They're going too far!

230
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,360
They're breaking

231
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,440
labor laws

232
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,440
and ignoring

233
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,120
local rules!

234
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:40,840
It's not just dodging responsibility.

235
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,270
They're disgracing Shenzhen!

236
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,790
Gao Xiang?

237
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,080
You're awake.

238
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,870
Sorry, didn't mean to wake you.

239
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:55,960
He's been here a while.

240
00:09:56,150 --> 00:09:57,000
As soon as I got the news

241
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:57,790
in Zhuhai,

242
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,030
I hurried back.

243
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:00,630
But I'm still late.

244
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,080
If I see that manager,

245
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,630
I'll give him

246
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,550
a piece of my mind.

247
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,360
The sun's up.

248
00:10:08,390 --> 00:10:10,030
Why isn't the surgery done yet?

249
00:10:10,670 --> 00:10:11,440
Don't worry.

250
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:14,320
Are you hungry?

251
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,320
You two go get some food.

252
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,000
I'll be here.

253
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,750
No.

254
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,120
I'm gonna

255
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,440
prepare legal documents.

256
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:34,120
And I'll take it

257
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:34,670
to arbitration.

258
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,960
Then court if needed.

259
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,120
Anyway,

260
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:38,550
we'll protect

261
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,510
Zhao Jun's rights.

262
00:10:41,960 --> 00:10:43,390
The doctor told me

263
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,840
success in surgery

264
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,840
doesn't mean she'll fully recover.

265
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:50,910
I didn't tell He Xiaoju.

266
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,150
I made the call myself.

267
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,480
Zhao Jun is young.

268
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,390
If she can't

269
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:02,720
live a normal life...

270
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,720
Don't worry too much.

271
00:11:34,550 --> 00:11:35,630
Jun, eat some.

272
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,600
Just have a little, okay?

273
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,360
Not eating?

274
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:47,630
You have to eat.

275
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,910
You need nutrition.

276
00:11:50,030 --> 00:11:53,080
The doctor said the surgery went well.

277
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,630
Thanks, Auntie.

278
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:05,240
Just eat.

279
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,480
The doctor said

280
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:08,320
the surgery was successful.

281
00:12:09,390 --> 00:12:10,000
But how well

282
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,120
you recover

283
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,600
depends on follow-up care.

284
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,630
That includes rest and nutrition.

285
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,080
And you need to

286
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,120
stay positive.

287
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,080
Zhao Jun,

288
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,840
the rest is up to you.

289
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,240
Come on.

290
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,270
Have a bite.

291
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:36,670
Also,

292
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:38,480
I need to tell

293
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,150
He Xiaoju and Zhao Dazhi.

294
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,200
They're your parents.

295
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,150
They have a right to know

296
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:46,270
and a duty to care for you.

297
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,870
So,

298
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,200
even if you hold a grudge

299
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,120
over the past,

300
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:50,480
you...

301
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,480
No grudge.

302
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,630
I'm just afraid they can't handle it.

303
00:12:55,670 --> 00:12:57,790
Honestly, my parents do love me.

304
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,080
During the surgery,

305
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,630
I kept dreaming.

306
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,910
I dreamed about my mom

307
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:12,120
making me egg custard.

308
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:15,390
It was soft.

309
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,550
Half with soy sauce,

310
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:26,000
half with sugar.

311
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:29,080
My dad put me

312
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,600
on his shoulders.

313
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,200
I was so high up.

314
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,030
Everything looked so small.

315
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:41,960
Later,

316
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,630
Zhao Kai was born.

317
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,480
They didn't have time for me anymore.

318
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:54,960
Auntie,

319
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,270
please.

320
00:13:58,550 --> 00:13:59,550
Don't tell them.

321
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:01,550
I promise

322
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,510
no matter

323
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:05,240
what happens,

324
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,630
I...

325
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:09,840
My parents and I will never blame you.

326
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,200
Your work

327
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,200
is dangerous.

328
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,270
Why didn't you tell me?

329
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,200
I volunteered

330
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,960
to work on that line.

331
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,390
The pay was better.

332
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,750
Now,

333
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,360
you just have to listen to the doctor.

334
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:33,030
Eat well and follow the treatment.

335
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,750
Once you're better,

336
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,000
everything will be just like before.

337
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,000
Impossible.

338
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,270
Things will never be the same.

339
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,720
Workplace injury?

340
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,240
Is it serious?

341
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,200
Four fingers

342
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:02,480
on her right hand were severed.

343
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:06,240
She's your niece?

344
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,750
My second sister's kid.

345
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,240
She left home young to work.

346
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,910
The line she worked on was dangerous.

347
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,200
But I didn't know.

348
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,630
Is there anything

349
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:20,480
we can do to help?

350
00:15:21,150 --> 00:15:21,670
No need.

351
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,360
The surgery went well.

352
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:25,480
But I missed

353
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:27,150
half a day of work

354
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:29,080
and the morning meeting.

355
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:31,000
I'll stay late

356
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:32,030
and make up the work.

357
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,870
Here's 200,000 RMB.

358
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:36,750
Take it.

359
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:37,720
No.

360
00:15:38,630 --> 00:15:39,720
I can't take your money.

361
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,320
That's workplace injury.

362
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,200
The factory will cover the costs.

363
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:46,910
Your niece must be very young.

364
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,480
After something like this,

365
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:49,550
she will

366
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,670
need money to get by.

367
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:52,000
This is just a small token.

368
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:52,750
Take it.

369
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,030
My niece and I

370
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,440
really appreciate your kindness.

371
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:56,550
However,

372
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:58,030
I can't accept it.

373
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,030
I'll get back to work.

374
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:31,320
President Yan.

375
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:32,720
Where do you want to eat?

376
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:33,630
Need me to set it up?

377
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:34,960
No plans tonight.

378
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:41,440
Take care of yourself.

379
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:42,790
Work can wait

380
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:43,960
until tomorrow.

381
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:05,070
Fang Wanzhi is still working?

382
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,030
She's got

383
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:09,070
a solid work attitude.

384
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,510
Her first time asking for leave.

385
00:17:12,960 --> 00:17:14,160
A girl from the mountains

386
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:16,000
is tough.

387
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:17,590
She's working hard

388
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:20,400
to build a life for herself
and her family.

389
00:17:21,510 --> 00:17:22,480
It's not easy.

390
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,550
Her niece must be pretty young?

391
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:28,480
She took the risky job

392
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,200
for the extra pay,

393
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,160
and now she's disabled.

394
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:34,830
Guess Fang Wanzhi has to support her.

395
00:17:36,350 --> 00:17:37,510
She didn't take the check.

396
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:38,440
Really?

397
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:41,200
That actually surprises me.

398
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:44,920
When did you

399
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,790
fall for her?

400
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:49,880
I'm your cousin.

401
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,240
I watched you grow up.

402
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,480
You think you can hide things from me?

403
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:56,240
I'm still not sure

404
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,310
if I like her.

405
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,310
But compared to the girls

406
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,720
you sent,

407
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:05,880
I don't dislike her.

408
00:18:06,070 --> 00:18:07,440
You know what Auntie

409
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,310
cares about most.

410
00:18:08,750 --> 00:18:09,550
Better get moving.

411
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,440
I don't agree with her plan.

412
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,920
It's not fair to Fang Wanzhi.

413
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,160
Seems like you feel more

414
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,590
than just liking her.

415
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:18,640
She said no to your check,

416
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:19,830
but the reason

417
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,160
is probably that the figure

418
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,590
wasn't what she expected.

419
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,960
Auntie's plan might be

420
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:26,270
a bit harsh on the woman.

421
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:28,160
But it's a dream

422
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,270
for many girls.

423
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:32,000
Auntie's been through a lot.

424
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:33,310
She knows

425
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:34,590
what having

426
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:35,590
enough money

427
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,510
means for a girl.

428
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:38,030
Put another way,

429
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:40,270
you might actually be helping her,

430
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,310
or even saving her.

431
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,200
Alright, Ms. Yao.

432
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:44,400
Not the same route.

433
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:46,480
I can't drive you.

434
00:18:49,550 --> 00:18:50,680
Get Fang Wanzhi

435
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:52,440
some midnight snack.

436
00:18:53,590 --> 00:18:54,270
Okay.

437
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:07,400
Ms. Yao.

438
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,350
Here.

439
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:11,000
Eat something.

440
00:19:12,030 --> 00:19:12,790
I'm not hungry.

441
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:14,720
President Yan asked me

442
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,510
to bring this.

443
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:17,750
Thanks.

444
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:18,880
He told me

445
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,400
your niece got hurt.

446
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:24,110
Just go home and take care of her.

447
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:25,440
I'll cover the rest

448
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:26,160
for you.

449
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:26,960
No need.

450
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,000
Almost done.

451
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,880
You know, Hongtu has

452
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,680
many subsidiaries.

453
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:33,510
And plenty of

454
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,790
easier positions too.

455
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,590
Pick one for your niece.

456
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,240
She can start once she's healed.

457
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,790
I couldn't possibly.

458
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:43,590
This is also from President Yan.

459
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:44,790
And I agree.

460
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:46,480
Your niece

461
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,480
must take after you.

462
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,350
Diligent and responsible.

463
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:01,480
She's asleep.

464
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:04,400
How's she?

465
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,070
The doctor changed her dressing

466
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:08,030
and said the surgery was successful.

467
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,590
Even better than expected.

468
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,480
That's good.

469
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:12,720
Wait.

470
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:14,920
You worked the whole day.

471
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,030
Why did you come?

472
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:17,920
I'm worried.

473
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:20,270
Your niece is my niece.

474
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:21,550
No need to worry.

475
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:23,440
Go home.

476
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:26,160
You've been here all day.

477
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,030
Let me take over.

478
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,750
I'm free these days.

479
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:29,960
Go now.

480
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,240
Juan.

481
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,440
Thank you.

482
00:20:38,790 --> 00:20:39,400
Go home.

483
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,000
Bye.

484
00:20:45,790 --> 00:20:47,270
Come in, Jun.

485
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:53,510
Go.

486
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,030
Lie down on the bed.

487
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,200
Auntie Juan,

488
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,030
I'm fine now.

489
00:20:59,590 --> 00:21:01,030
No, you're not.

490
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,590
Just five days,

491
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,550
and you're discharged.

492
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:05,270
Listen to me. Just lie down.

493
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,240
Don't do anything.

494
00:21:06,790 --> 00:21:07,200
Come on.

495
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:08,720
Be good.

496
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:10,160
Lie down.

497
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:12,550
Your foot.

498
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:14,720
You're both home?

499
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:15,830
Aren't you at work?

500
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,200
Why come back?

501
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:20,200
I knew

502
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,200
you had no time to cook.

503
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,440
So I grabbed some takeout.

504
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:23,510
Actually,

505
00:21:23,510 --> 00:21:24,720
I should've made you a meal.

506
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:26,200
Fine.

507
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,510
We'll have this for lunch.

508
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:28,590
I'll make you

509
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,680
bone broth tonight.

510
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:30,680
And chicken soup

511
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:31,440
tomorrow morning.

512
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,000
Okay?

513
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:38,920
He Yongwang?

514
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,030
Mr. He?

515
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,590
You came alone?

516
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:46,920
And Zhao Jun's parents?

517
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,070
Grandpa!

518
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:50,400
Jun!

519
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:53,270
Jun!

520
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:56,510
Let me see your hand.

521
00:21:59,590 --> 00:22:00,680
It must hurt!

522
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:04,070
Oh, poor girl.

523
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,750
Why come so far to work?

524
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,270
What if

525
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:08,550
you're disabled?

526
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:13,640
Grandpa,

527
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,640
disability doesn't mean inability.

528
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,750
Don't talk like that.

529
00:22:18,070 --> 00:22:19,160
Auntie and I don't like it.

530
00:22:19,510 --> 00:22:20,160
Mr. He,

531
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,200
the doctor reattached

532
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:23,030
her fingers.

533
00:22:23,480 --> 00:22:24,160
Reattached them?

534
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,880
That must have cost a lot.

535
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,960
You don't have to pay anyway.

536
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:30,750
How do you know this?

537
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,110
Yang Hui told me.

538
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:38,270
And he bought my ticket.

539
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,550
Yang Hui?

540
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:41,070
I didn't tell him.

541
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:42,480
My bad.

542
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,200
A few days ago,

543
00:22:44,590 --> 00:22:46,030
Yang Hui called me.

544
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:48,400
I just couldn't hold back.

545
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,160
Not your fault.

546
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:50,960
Her parents

547
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,110
should know this.

548
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,480
What good would that do?

549
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,790
They wouldn't come.

550
00:22:57,030 --> 00:22:59,160
Jun, don't blame them.

551
00:22:59,550 --> 00:23:01,160
Something big is happening back home.

552
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,000
They're helping Zhao Kai

553
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:03,960
find a job.

554
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,790
Money's already been spent.

555
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:06,920
Almost done with it.

556
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,350
Once he's employed,

557
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,830
they need to host a dinner
to return the favor.

558
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,510
They really couldn't get away.

559
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:16,480
Your mom

560
00:23:16,750 --> 00:23:17,350
made all this

561
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,750
for you.

562
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,680
When she heard,

563
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,590
she cried for hours.

564
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:23,830
Jun,

565
00:23:24,350 --> 00:23:25,000
this is all

566
00:23:26,110 --> 00:23:27,750
I can do for you.

567
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:28,920
Take it.

568
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:30,310
No, Grandpa.

569
00:23:30,550 --> 00:23:30,920
Take it.

570
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:31,750
I won't take it.

571
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:35,480
Take it. It's just a small token.

572
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,000
As long as you heal,

573
00:23:39,350 --> 00:23:40,510
I'll be at peace.

574
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:44,270
I'm off.

575
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:52,200
Where are you going?

576
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:55,510
Shenxian Peak.

577
00:23:56,590 --> 00:23:57,440
I can't just

578
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,480
leave my old body here

579
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,000
to rot.

580
00:24:31,550 --> 00:24:32,160
He Yongwang!

581
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:33,550
Give it to me.

582
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:36,350
Can't do that.

583
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:37,070
Give me that.

584
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:39,880
What are you after?

585
00:24:42,830 --> 00:24:43,510
It's dirty.

586
00:24:44,480 --> 00:24:45,880
You coughed up blood!

587
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,160
When did this start?

588
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,750
A few months ago.

589
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,400
I saw a doctor

590
00:24:52,590 --> 00:24:55,030
and took many pills, but nothing helped.

591
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,750
They all say I'm dying.

592
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:00,110
Yang Hui's dad

593
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:01,920
and Zhao Kai's dad talked it over.

594
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:04,310
They'll buy me a coffin.

595
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:07,070
After all, I have no son.

596
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,680
Stop talking about that. It's useless.

597
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,790
Did the doctor say what it is?

598
00:25:11,070 --> 00:25:12,070
Did you get an X-ray?

599
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:17,160
I don't have much time left.

600
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,590
Last month I couldn't even get out of bed.

601
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:23,070
Your two sisters took care of me.

602
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:24,790
Or I would have died.

603
00:25:25,030 --> 00:25:27,240
Then I wouldn't have seen Zhao Jun

604
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:31,030
suffer so much.

605
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,200
Sorry, President Yan.

606
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,550
I need another day off.

607
00:25:42,550 --> 00:25:43,830
My elder suddenly came.

608
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,240
He's not well.

609
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:46,680
We're in the hospital now.

610
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,270
Yes.

611
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:50,830
Right.

612
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:52,880
Thank you.

613
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:57,400
(Next, He Yongwang!)

614
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,000
Time for your X-ray.

615
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:04,960
X-ray?

616
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:06,240
Just a waste of money.

617
00:26:07,070 --> 00:26:07,830
Where do I go?

618
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:12,200
Where's the patient?

619
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,640
He's outside.

620
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,030
He's elderly.

621
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,720
I worry the diagnosis will crush him.

622
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:18,830
Just pneumonia.

623
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:20,110
He can handle it.

624
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,270
Get an IV first and take medicine on time.

625
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,440
Most importantly,

626
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,750
quit smoking.

627
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,160
I smelled smoke

628
00:26:27,510 --> 00:26:28,640
the moment he walked in.

629
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:29,720
And it's not even

630
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:31,240
real cigarettes.

631
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:44,270
100 yuan for dropping cigarette butts.

632
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:48,310
Well, I didn't want to throw it away.

633
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,720
There's still a lot left.

634
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:51,440
Hand over all your cigarettes.

635
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,680
Put them in.

636
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,000
Any more?

637
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,000
Yes.

638
00:27:05,750 --> 00:27:06,350
Put them in.

639
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:08,830
This...

640
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:10,720
This is still whole. Haven't rolled it.

641
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,310
In the bag.

642
00:27:16,590 --> 00:27:17,160
None left?

643
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:18,750
None left.

644
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:19,750
Really?

645
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,200
Really!

646
00:27:22,270 --> 00:27:23,790
Your eyes give you away.

647
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:24,750
No lying.

648
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,160
Put every last cigarette

649
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:26,880
in this.

650
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:27,480
No...

651
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:30,310
And this.

652
00:27:30,480 --> 00:27:31,030
Right.

653
00:27:31,550 --> 00:27:32,830
This is expensive.

654
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,070
This is

655
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,480
for guests.

656
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,070
Yang Hui bought it for me.

657
00:27:37,110 --> 00:27:37,790
With filters.

658
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:39,510
Yang Hui bought you cigarettes?

659
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:39,960
Yeah.

660
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,440
I'll give him an earful.

661
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:42,310
Put it in.

662
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,510
And that pouch.

663
00:27:43,550 --> 00:27:44,070
I saw it.

664
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,000
Everything in.

665
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:48,070
Oh, you have sharp eyes.

666
00:27:48,310 --> 00:27:49,200
Alright, everything.

667
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,400
Put it in.

668
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:53,160
Wait.

669
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,350
What are you doing?

670
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:58,070
You...

671
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:59,400
Why did you throw them away?

672
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:01,030
Principal Fang spoiled you.

673
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,070
No rules for you, huh?

674
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:04,920
You're very sick.

675
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:05,880
You have to quit.

676
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,480
I don't have long left anyway.

677
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,200
Why put me through that misery?

678
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,880
Cigarettes mean more to you than living?

679
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:14,030
My life is worthless.

680
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:15,550
They mean more to you than me?

681
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:18,640
He Yongwang,

682
00:28:19,030 --> 00:28:19,960
if you quit smoking,

683
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,830
I'll forgive you

684
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:23,350
for the past.

685
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,310
Seriously?

686
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:37,030
You would really forgive me?

687
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:19,000
Why are you lying here?

688
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,960
I still woke you up

689
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,550
Go to your room.

690
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:27,070
I made up a bed for you.

691
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:29,830
That bed is too clean.

692
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,160
I couldn't lie in it.

693
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:32,110
Besides,

694
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:34,400
