695
00:29:35,030 --> 00:29:36,400
I would wake you up.

696
00:29:36,830 --> 00:29:37,640
You won't.

697
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,110
If you do,

698
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:40,160
I'll let you know.

699
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:42,310
I'm fine out here.

700
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:44,510
By the way,

701
00:29:45,030 --> 00:29:45,920
there's nothing

702
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,350
