705
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:53,440
Not really.

706
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:53,960
Well,

707
00:29:54,350 --> 00:29:55,960
if you hadn't thrown those away...

708
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,590
Just kidding.

709
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:01,590
Sorry.

710
00:30:02,030 --> 00:30:03,350
I wasted a lot of paper.

711
00:30:03,960 --> 00:30:04,790
Go sleep inside.

712
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,480
Use tissues when you cough.

713
00:30:07,070 --> 00:30:08,510
If you really want a cigarette...

714
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:09,030
I don't.

715
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,160
I'll hold it in.

716
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:13,480
Go get some rest.

717
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,550
You need to work tomorrow.

718
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,400
You earn hundreds a day.

719
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:19,110
It would be a crime to disturb you.

720
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,110
What is it?

721
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:37,680
Not going in?

722
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,790
Then I'll sleep here.

723
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,070
That won't do.

724
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,110
Oh, you... well.

725
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,830
You've got ways.

726
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,000
Alright, I'm going now.

727
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:50,480
I'm inside.

728
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,270
Come in.

729
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:03,880
I won't accept

730
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:04,960
Yan Ziwei's check.

731
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:06,720
But for Zhao Jun,

732
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:08,200
a job at Hongtu

733
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:09,750
would be

734
00:31:09,750 --> 00:31:11,000
a great opportunity.

735
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,310
Right.

736
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,440
With hope for the future,

737
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:16,030
her mood will improve.

738
00:31:16,270 --> 00:31:17,350
Then her fingers

739
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:18,790
will heal faster.

740
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,640
That's what the doctor said.

741
00:31:24,030 --> 00:31:26,960
Well, Yan Ziwei

742
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:28,720
offered you an apartment first,

743
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:30,830
then when he knew your family got hurt,

744
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:31,960
he gave you a check.

745
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:33,310
Now he's even getting Zhao Jun

746
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:34,200
a job.

747
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,110
His intentions are pretty clear.

748
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,790
He's just good to his employees.

749
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:41,790
You really buy that?

750
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:43,310
Why hasn't he

751
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,720
done this for anyone else?

752
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,200
Alright,

753
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:47,550
I've already accepted

754
00:31:47,590 --> 00:31:49,110
