755
00:31:49,310 --> 00:31:50,270
Don't talk nonsense.

756
00:31:50,350 --> 00:31:51,400
It's not nonsense.

757
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,400
The second

758
00:31:52,400 --> 00:31:53,880
you chose to move,

759
00:31:54,070 --> 00:31:55,400
you already knew.

760
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,240
No.

761
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:59,440
The main reason I moved

762
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:01,240
was to help Liu Zhu find Hao Qianqian.

763
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:03,240
And it's closer to work.

764
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,310
Well, fine.

765
00:32:04,510 --> 00:32:05,440
Everyone needs

766
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:06,590
an excuse sometimes.

767
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:07,790
Li Juan, you...

768
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,030
I haven't asked you.

769
00:32:10,110 --> 00:32:11,350
How's Mr. He doing?

770
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,270
Everything okay?

771
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,200
When I left,

772
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,030
he was still asleep.

773
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:17,790
He'll get used to it.

774
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:18,550
Good.

775
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,590
Then I'll look after

776
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:22,160
Zhao Jun and Mr. He these days.

777
00:32:22,270 --> 00:32:23,400
But I'm busy on Friday.

778
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:24,790
I have to handle a shipment

779
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,920
at Guangzhou station.

780
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:27,030
I'll request time off.

781
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,750
I really fell asleep.

782
00:32:48,310 --> 00:32:49,750
Never slept

783
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,590
in a place this nice.

784
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,830
So cozy.

785
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,440
Wanzhi?

786
00:33:07,510 --> 00:33:08,270
Wanzhi?

787
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:12,960
Off to work already?

788
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:16,070
Though the pay is high,

789
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:18,270
she needs to work long hours.

790
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,310
Good morning.

791
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,240
Good morning.

792
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:22,840
Shenzhen is so clean.

793
00:34:27,030 --> 00:34:27,400
Morning.

794
00:34:27,630 --> 00:34:28,150
Morning.

795
00:34:28,670 --> 00:34:29,230
Hey, man,

796
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:30,880
excuse me.

797
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:31,920
Sorry to bother you.

798
00:34:32,190 --> 00:34:33,230
Where can I find

799
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:35,400
a convenience store?

800
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:37,960
What do you need to buy?

801
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:38,880
I wanna buy...

802
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,230
Gotta see it first.

803
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,360
Then I'll know.

804
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:43,710
There's no convenience store

805
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,440
in our neighborhood.

806
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:47,030
But the bar

807
00:34:47,030 --> 00:34:47,840
in our clubhouse

808
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:49,280
has a pretty good selection.

809
00:34:49,630 --> 00:34:51,630
Drinks, alcohol,

810
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:52,800
cigarettes, you name it.

811
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:53,880
That's great!

812
00:34:55,030 --> 00:34:56,480
Where's the clubhouse?

813
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,590
Would you mind showing me the way?

814
00:34:58,710 --> 00:34:59,190
Of course.

815
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:00,070
Come with me.

816
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:00,960
Thank you.

817
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:02,630
People in Shenzhen are so friendly.

818
00:35:04,670 --> 00:35:06,550
Sir, I don't think I've seen you around.

819
00:35:06,710 --> 00:35:08,320
Did you just move here?

820
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:09,550
I'm not worthy of

821
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:11,000
a place this nice.

822
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,710
I'm just here thanks to my daughter.

823
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,920
She works at a big company.

824
00:35:15,510 --> 00:35:16,800
She lives over there.

825
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:19,070
Building 18, Apartment 202.

826
00:35:19,230 --> 00:35:20,630
Her boss provides it.

827
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,630
It's very big

828
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:23,440
and spotless.

829
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:25,880
It's him.

830
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,400
Got it, Mr. Yan.

831
00:35:27,550 --> 00:35:28,070
I'm on it.

832
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,400
Good morning, sir.

833
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:33,320
Morning.

834
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:33,960
Sorry,

835
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:34,840
we're not open yet.

836
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:35,960
Need something?

837
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:37,070
I can help you out.

838
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,230
Oh, I couldn't possibly.

839
00:35:39,550 --> 00:35:42,000
I just wanna take a look at...

840
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:43,280
cigarettes.

841
00:35:43,590 --> 00:35:43,960
Here.

842
00:35:46,510 --> 00:35:47,360
How much is it?

843
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:48,150
That?

844
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,030
Fifty.

845
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:51,630
And this?

846
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:52,800
Twenty-five.

847
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:55,070
Cigarettes here are really expensive.

848
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,280
Mr. Yan

849
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,000
told me

850
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:57,920
he's covering

851
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,110
your bills.

852
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,670
Mr. Yan?

853
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,230
The man

854
00:36:02,230 --> 00:36:03,190
who brought you here.

855
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:04,550
That's too much!

856
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:06,280
I don't even know him.

857
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:07,190
Just asked him,

858
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,670
and he walked me over.

859
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:11,070
I can't let him pay for it.

860
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:32,230
(He Yongwang,)

861
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:33,510
if you quit smoking,

862
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,510
I'll forgive you

863
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:36,880
for the past.

864
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:48,000
President Yan.

865
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:52,630
Good morning.

866
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:53,400
Morning.

867
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,230
Good morning.

868
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,360
Sorry,

869
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,630
I took a leave yesterday.

870
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,510
Why did you come so early?

871
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,590
Shouldn't you be with

872
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:06,710
your sick elder?

873
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:08,840
The doctor said it's not serious.

874
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:10,630
By the way,

875
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:11,670
I'm gonna

876
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:12,840
need next Friday off.

877
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:14,360
My niece has a follow-up,

878
00:37:14,630 --> 00:37:15,670
and my elder needs an IV.

879
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:16,880
Sure.

880
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:17,920
Thanks.

881
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,230
The last few times,

882
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:29,000
it was Li Juan who brought me here.

883
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,710
She's smart.

884
00:37:32,670 --> 00:37:35,320
She knows she works for

885
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:36,320
the one who pays her.

886
00:37:36,670 --> 00:37:38,150
It's not about the pay.

887
00:37:38,550 --> 00:37:39,880
She's my best friend.

888
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,670
But she's not your family.

889
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:44,710
I figured it out this time.

890
00:37:45,670 --> 00:37:46,360
You work at

891
00:37:46,510 --> 00:37:48,840
a big company now.

892
00:37:49,070 --> 00:37:50,320
And Li Juan is running

893
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:52,070
your old business.

894
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,710
You trust her that much?

895
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,110
Why wouldn't I?

896
00:37:55,590 --> 00:37:56,150
I said

897
00:37:56,190 --> 00:37:57,630
she's my best friend.

898
00:37:58,190 --> 00:37:59,360
Just as good as a real sister.

899
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:02,000
Wait until something big happens.

900
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:04,070
I may not be capable,

901
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,710
but I've seen more than you have.

902
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:08,280
Not sure

903
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:09,840
if I should say this.

904
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,150
I heard her

905
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:13,320
on the phone.

906
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,360
Shipments worth over 100,000 RMB,

907
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,510
and she travels

908
00:38:18,550 --> 00:38:20,360
with bags full of cash.

909
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,030
You seriously trust her?

910
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:23,070
Well,

911
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,030
Zhao Jun

912
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,590
has been by your side

913
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:28,710
for a few years.

914
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:32,360
She's honest.

915
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,230
She's your family anyway.

916
00:38:34,760 --> 00:38:35,440
You should

917
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:37,110
trust Zhao Jun.

918
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,840
If you're unsure whether to say it,

919
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,760
better not.

920
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,280
Come on.

921
00:38:44,550 --> 00:38:47,150
Zhao Jun is disabled now.

922
00:38:47,440 --> 00:38:49,150
Physical work is no longer

923
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:50,000
an option.

924
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,230
You're her aunt.

925
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:55,110
Help her if you can.

926
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,630
No matter how good Li Juan is,

927
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:59,030
can she beat family?

928
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,030
Is family really always the best?

929
00:39:05,030 --> 00:39:06,280
Don't say that again,

930
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,480
or I'll turn on you.

931
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:16,760
The doctor praised me.

932
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:18,440
He said I'm recovering well.

933
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,440
Thanks to you and Auntie Juan.

934
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:23,670
Oh,

935
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:24,710
and my grandpa.

936
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,590
I did nothing.

937
00:39:38,030 --> 00:39:39,920
So much takeout!

938
00:39:40,110 --> 00:39:41,320
Why didn't you just cook?

939
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:43,150
No time to cook.

940
00:39:43,760 --> 00:39:44,960
It's too wasteful.

941
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:46,670
My mom called me.

942
00:39:47,550 --> 00:39:49,230
She's happy

943
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:49,960
the surgery

944
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:51,710
and recovery went well.

945
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,190
What else did she say?

946
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,710
She wants me home to get married.

947
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,670
No bride price.

948
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:57,840
I can pick any guy

949
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:58,800
in Yu County.

950
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,760
She's confident

951
00:40:01,030 --> 00:40:01,960
in my looks.

952
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:04,190
What's your plan?

953
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:06,030
I love Yu County.

954
00:40:06,710 --> 00:40:07,920
And I love Shenxian Peak.

955
00:40:08,110 --> 00:40:09,190
But I don't want to leave.

956
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:10,710
I want to be like you

957
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,440
and make it

958
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:13,360
in Shenzhen.

959
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:16,400
I haven't made it yet.

960
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:18,630
If you want to stay in Shenzhen,

961
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:19,710
rest a few days,

962
00:40:19,710 --> 00:40:21,000
then come work at Hongtu.

963
00:40:21,190 --> 00:40:22,510
Quality inspection

964
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:23,400
suits you.

965
00:40:24,030 --> 00:40:24,670
No!

966
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:25,320
I chose that

967
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,670
especially for you.

968
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:27,760
It's safe work.

969
00:40:28,110 --> 00:40:29,760
And fits your situation right now.

970
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:30,880
I know.

971
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:32,190
Thanks, Auntie.

972
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:34,800
But I'm done working for others.

973
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:35,840
I wanna open a store

974
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:36,800
and work for myself.

975
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:38,710
Just like you did

976
00:40:38,710 --> 00:40:39,480
at Dongmen.

977
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,480
A store?

978
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,400
I've saved some money.

979
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,360
But it's not enough.

980
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,360
Would you

981
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,400
be my major investor?

982
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,710
Which location?

983
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,110
Right here in Buji Town.

984
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:53,230
Lots of people pass through here.

985
00:40:53,510 --> 00:40:54,440
And most of them

986
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:55,800
are migrant workers like us.

987
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,920
I know their habits

988
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:58,960
and budget.

989
00:40:59,150 --> 00:41:01,230
If we're open around the clock,

990
00:41:01,440 --> 00:41:02,510
business should be good.

991
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,880
A few of my classmates

992
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,510
work as suppliers.

993
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:07,030
They'll let me delay payments.

994
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:07,880
So,

995
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,280
cash flow won't be a problem.

996
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:12,440
Auntie,

997
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,630
invest in me.

998
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,110
First year,

999
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,590
money back.

1000
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:17,670
Second year, double.

1001
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:19,510
Investing isn't that simple.

1002
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,320
Show me

1003
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:22,400
your business plan.

1004
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,400
I'm already writing it.

1005
00:41:25,190 --> 00:41:25,960
What plan?

1006
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,190
Am I in it?

1007
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:27,920
Grandpa,

1008
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,360
you already finished your IV.

1009
00:41:30,590 --> 00:41:31,360
Not going back?

1010
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,480
I'll buy you a plane ticket.

1011
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,550
A plane?

1012
00:41:34,920 --> 00:41:36,320
Then I'd be going to heaven.

1013
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,190
Nonsense!

1014
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,000
Since you're here,

1015
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:42,110
stay at least three months

1016
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,400
and quit smoking.

1017
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,030
The president's still here,

1018
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,630
and the assistant already left?

1019
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:08,320
She asked for leave today.

1020
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:16,150
You two

1021
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:18,280
look pretty good together.

1022
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:24,400
Though, in my heart,

1023
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:25,760
no one's good enough

1024
00:42:26,230 --> 00:42:27,960
for my handsome cousin.

1025
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:29,550
You're so bored?

1026
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:30,840
Not as bored as you.

1027
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,230
She's gone,

1028
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:33,670
and you're looking at photos.

1029
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:35,840
Still won't admit you like her?

1030
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,840
Seize the moment if you wanna pursue her.

1031
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:39,630
Her niece

1032
00:42:39,630 --> 00:42:40,710
just got injured at work.

1033
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:42,440
Her dad came to Shenzhen for treatment.

1034
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:43,630
That's just an excuse.

1035
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:45,190
Money's the point.

1036
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:46,320
We should...

1037
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:47,960
That's not seizing the moment.

1038
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,880
That's profiting from her pain.
